The map has been updated to it's second final version (I know that doesnt really make sence), this version has the bug removed where the t can go to the mgs when they spawn. Thanks for downloading.

This is death run Family Guy! The map is of a medium size and will run and play well on all server sizes. The map has: 64 spawn points (2T, 62CT) 18 traps which are as follows: 1. Mad Stewie Gunman 2. Peter, letting one off 3. Evil monkey 4. Street crusher 5. Platforms…. OF DEATH 6. Herbert’s walkers 7. Meg, do you feel me inside of you? 8. Have you got your poison? 9. Louis on a rampage 10. Sewer going dry 11. Cash attack! 12. Back alley platforms 13. Special dad all game 14. Blue n Red doors 15. Brian’s road side bomb 16. Stone age invention 17. Stewie’s force 18. This weighs a ton 3 MGs 1. Druggy Fight 2. Sewer Bhop 3. Old 3 Secret nades 1. Peters trail 2. Feels like Brian 3. Magical FCC music nade The map also has an AFK spawn killer and a lot of custom textures. Included in the download is a copy of the .bsp and also a .bz2. Happy death running!
